column2: Has anyone ever: Attacked you with a gun, knife, stick, bottle, or other weapon?
Has anyone ever: Hurt you by striking or beating you to the point that you had bruises, cuts, or broken bones or otherwise physically abused you?
Has anyone ever: Pressured or forced you to participate in sexual acts against your will, including your regular sexual partner, a family member, or friend?
Has anyone ever: Abused you emotionally; that is, did or said things to make you feel very bad about yourself or your life?
Has anyone ever: About how old were you the first time any of these things happened to you?
Has anyone ever: About how old were you the first time any of these things happened to you? Is e under 18?
Did any of the previous things happen: several times or over a long period of time?
Did any of the previous things happen: with more than one person involved in hurting you?
Did any of the previous things happen: where one or more of the people involved was a family member, close family friend, professional, or someone else you had trusted?
Did any of the previous things happen: where you were afraid for your life or that you might be seriously injured?
Did any of the previous things happen: and result in oral, vaginal, or anal sex?
Did any of the previous things happen: and people you told did not believe or help you?
Are you currently worried that someone might . . . attack you with a gun, knife, stick, bottle, or other weapon?
Are you currently worried that someone might . . . hurt you by striking or beating or otherwise physically abuse you?
Are you currently worried that someone might . . . pressure or force you to participate in sexual acts against your will?
Are you currently worried that someone might . . . abuse you emotionally?
